    "description": "Abomifighters: World League is a local coop and online brawler game for up to 4 players. You assemble your character from different body parts and fight your way to victory!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1788130/extras/a7701daf83251141bc2e37eea44c5538.poster.avif?t=1713508018\" width=600 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1788130/extras/a7701daf83251141bc2e37eea44c5538.webm?t=1713508018\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1788130/extras/a7701daf83251141bc2e37eea44c5538.mp4?t=1713508018\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>• Build absolutely crazy characters. Attach anything to anything: sharkosaurus, broccocopter, zombiecentaurus – it’s up to you to create your own avatar.<br>• Unique character creation system: Each limb changes the way you move and fight. You can punch out limbs from your enemies, pick it to retain their abilities and recreate your avatar right in the game.<br>• Crazy levels: Avoid traps and collect power ups in real world-like levels. <br>• Co-op or Free-For-All: Team up with your friends and fight with your enemies online. Or be friends with no one in ruthless free for all fights!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1788130/extras/8344ad05cecedab3fa4fa02fbc8ff3e1.poster.avif?t=1713508018\" width=600 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1788130/extras/8344ad05cecedab3fa4fa02fbc8ff3e1.webm?t=1713508018\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1788130/extras/8344ad05cecedab3fa4fa02fbc8ff3e1.mp4?t=1713508018\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
